	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For what you get, the PowerPAK is a reasonable price. 
<br />
<br />Old Chinese Game Copiers existed that in combination with Famicom Disk System could play specially hacked ROMs on Game Doctor formatted Famicom Disk System diskettes. But they are even more expensive than the PowerPAK and far less user friendly or useful.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
